      "variant": "main",
      "html": "<h4>Activity</h4>\n<p>A marine biologist estimates that a structure of coral has a volume of 1,200 cubic centimeters and that its volume doubles each year.</p>\n<p><img height=\"300\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/915e980323c039f033c1086572a5d1f032cef8c3\" width=\"300\"></p>\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"Reveal1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\">\n      <li>Write an equation of the form \\(y=a\\cdot b^t\\) representing the relationship, where \\(t\\)&nbsp;is time in years since the coral was measured and \\(y\\)&nbsp;is volume of coral in cubic centimeters. (You need to figure out what numbers \\(a\\) and \\(b\\)&nbsp;are in this situation.)</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <p>Write down your answer, then select the <strong>Solution</strong> button to compare your work.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-content\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"Reveal1\">\n  <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n  <p>\\(y=1,200\\cdot 2^t\\)</p>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"Reveal1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\">\n      <li>Find the volume of the coral when \\(t\\)&nbsp;is 5, 1, 0, &ndash;1, and &ndash;2. Note that when \\(t = -1\\), this represents one year before the marine biologist made the original estimate.<br><br>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n    <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n      <colgroup>\n        <col width=\"153\">\n        <col width=\"78\">\n        <col width=\"77\">\n        <col width=\"71\">\n        <col width=\"65\">\n        <col width=\"60\">\n      </colgroup>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <p>time (years)</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <p>5</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <p>1</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <p>0</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <p>&ndash;1</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <p>&ndash;2</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <p>volume of coral (cubic centimeters)</p>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <p>Write down your answer, then select the <strong>Solution</strong> button to compare your work.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-content\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"Reveal1\">\n  <p>Compare your answers:</p>\n  <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    <colgroup>\n      <col width=\"153\">\n      <col width=\"78\">\n      <col width=\"77\">\n      <col width=\"71\">\n      <col width=\"65\">\n      <col width=\"60\">\n    </colgroup>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>time (years)</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>5</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>1</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>0</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>&ndash;1</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>&ndash;2</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>volume of coral (cubic centimeters)</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>38,400</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>2,400</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>1,200</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>600</p>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p>300</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"a279dee3-1ef1-44ac-8898-560fb004114a\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"3\">\n      <li>What does it mean, in this situation, when \\(t\\)&nbsp;is &ndash;2?</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p> This represents the time 2 years before the scientist made the estimate of 1,200 cubic centimeters.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"334f0620-d6a6-417c-b671-2eae1b10f7df\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"4\">\n      <li>In a certain year, the volume of the coral is 37.5 cubic centimeters. Which year is this? Explain your reasoning.</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>\\(t\\) is &ndash;5, or 5 years before the scientist made the estimate of 1,200 cubic centimeters.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->"
